revision.text:
{{codepointer|Sound}}void '''A_PlayWeaponSound''' (sound ''whattoplay'')

{{WarnDeprecated|{{c|[[A_StartSound]]}}}}


Plays the specified sound but uses the weapon channel. Sounds started with this function do not interfere with sounds played with {{c|[[A_StartSound]]}}, unless {{c|{{const|CHAN_WEAPON}}}} is passed as the used channel.
